      <p>Cold emailing brands for sponsorships works. It works better than waiting to be discovered, better than marketplace platforms that take commissions, and better than DM outreach that gets buried in message requests. The creators who earn consistent sponsorship income treat outreach as a weekly business activity with the same discipline they apply to content creation.</p>

